  "title": "Sequential Elimination Under Cost",
  "concept": "When testing cost is high and a hypothesis remains uncertain after initial probes, eliminating it entirely becomes cheaper than continuing to test.",
  "interactiveId": "17fad2fd-f3e1-4da2-950a-f51f9d87c79b",
  "sourcePieceId": "b77e8406-a000-46ef-8989-dde9bb48a8b4",
  "publishedAt": 1777734358435,
  "voiceScore": 90,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Sequential Elimination Under Cost</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --primary: #1a6b62;\n    --secondary: #c9a227;\n    --danger: #c93a27;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .control {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .control label {\n    font-weight: 500;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    min-width: 110px;\n  }\n  .control input[type=range] {\n    flex: 1;\n    accent-color: var(--primary);\n    min-width: 120px;\n  }\n  .control output {\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    min-width: 3ch;\n    text-align: right;\n  }\n  .comparison {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 16px;\n    margin: 24px 0 16px;\n  }\n  .path {\n    padding: 16px;\n    border: 2px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    background: #fff;\n    transition: all 200ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .path.cheaper {\n    border-color: var(--primary);\n    background: #f0f9f8;\n  }\n  .path-label {\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n  .path.cheaper .path-label {\n    color: var(--primary);\n  }\n  .cost-display {\n    font-size: 1.8rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    margin: 8px 0 12px;\n  }\n  .path-desc {\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  .threshold-line {\n    margin: 20px 0 12px;\n    padding: 12px 16px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .threshold-line strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  .threshold-marker {\n    height: 6px;\n    background: var(--line);\n    border-radius: 3px;\n    margin-top: 8px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .threshold-marker::after {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    left: var(--crossover, 50%);\n    top: -4px;\n    width: 2px;\n    height: 14px;\n    background: var(--danger);\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 520px) {\n    .comparison {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Adjust the cost per test</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">Two paths to narrow uncertainty: keep testing the leading explanation or eliminate it outright. One becomes cheaper as test cost rises.</p>\n\n<div class=\"control\">\n  <label for=\"test-cost\">Cost per test:</label>\n  <input id=\"test-cost\" type=\"range\" min=\"1\" max=\"10\" value=\"3\" step=\"1\" aria-describedby=\"test-cost-out\">\n  <output id=\"test-cost-out\" for=\"test-cost\">3</output>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"comparison\">\n  <div class=\"path\" id=\"path-test\">\n    <div class=\"path-label\">Continue testing</div>\n    <div class=\"cost-display\" id=\"cost-test\">12</div>\n    <div class=\"path-desc\">Run four more tests on the leading explanation. Each negative result narrows confidence.</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"path cheaper\" id=\"path-remove\">\n    <div class=\"path-label\">Eliminate & move on</div>\n    <div class=\"cost-display\" id=\"cost-remove\">8</div>\n    <div class=\"path-desc\">Remove the leading explanation from consideration. Certainty shifts to the next option.</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"threshold-line\">\n  Crossover at cost <strong id=\"crossover-val\">2</strong> per test.\n  <div class=\"threshold-marker\" id=\"marker\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">Below the crossover, testing is cheaper. Above it, elimination wins.</p>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  var slider = document.getElementById('test-cost');\n  var output = document.getElementById('test-cost-out');\n  var costTestEl = document.getElementById('cost-test');\n  var costRemoveEl = document.getElementById('cost-remove');\n  var pathTest = document.getElementById('path-test');\n  var pathRemove = document.getElementById('path-remove');\n  var crossoverVal = document.getElementById('crossover-val');\n  var marker = document.getElementById('marker');\n  var caption = document.getElementById('caption');\n\n  var testsNeeded = 4;\n  var eliminationCost = 8;\n  var crossover = eliminationCost / testsNeeded;\n\n  function update() {\n    var cost = +slider.value;\n    output.textContent = cost;\n    var testTotal = cost * testsNeeded;\n    costTestEl.textContent = testTotal;\n    costRemoveEl.textContent = eliminationCost;\n    crossoverVal.textContent = crossover.toFixed(1);\n\n    var crossoverPct = Math.min(100, Math.max(0, ((crossover - 1) / 9) * 100));\n    marker.style.setProperty('--crossover', crossoverPct + '%');\n\n    pathTest.classList.remove('cheaper');\n    pathRemove.classList.remove('cheaper');\n    if (testTotal < eliminationCost) {\n      pathTest.classList.add('cheaper');\n    } else {\n      pathRemove.classList.add('cheaper');\n    }\n\n    if (cost < crossover) {\n      caption.textContent = 'Below the crossover, testing is cheaper. Four tests cost less than eliminating the leading explanation outright.';\n    } else if (cost === Math.round(crossover)) {\n      caption.textContent = 'At the crossover, both paths cost the same. The choice is a wash.';\n    } else {\n      caption.textContent = 'Above the crossover, elimination wins. Removing the leading explanation costs less than continuing to test it.';\n    }\n  }\n\n  slider.addEventListener('input', update);\n  update();\n})();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
